title: My.Dream.Home.s03e03.PDTV.x264.Hector.mp4
description:
This show is called "Property Brothers" in some countries.
Please note that the episodes will soon be uploaded in a rather random order as that is the way Foxtel (my TV service) presents them! Luckily, you don't need to watch episode 8 before episode 9 etc!

Working long hours and eager to upgrade her starter home, April is looking to buy a new house in the downtown core. The Property Brothers come to the rescue and help her find a budget-friendly dream home that can be renovated on time.

If you see "Hector" on the end of a file it means I capped it.
Enjoy, Gaz/Hector :)
